courses.customDesc: One course from each of the following GE areas must be completed: A1, A2, A3, B1, B2, B3, (B4 [lab] must be completed with either B2 or B3), C1, C2, C3, C4, C1-C5 elective, D1, D3, D4, D5 and F. C4, D5 and F should be taken only after Junior standing is reached (90 units). NO ECON FOR D5. Refer to online catalog for GE course selection, United States Cultural Pluralism (USCP) and Graduation Writing Requirement (GWR). USCP requirement can be satisfied by some (but not all) courses with GE categories: C3, C4, D1, D3, D4, D5 or F.
Any free elective can go here. Recommended: BUS100.
